WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.350
In a dark corner, an endless lesson, and a mind drifting far away.

00:00:05.430 --> 00:00:12.137
But a mother saw what no one else did... she searched for another way, and found PlayVerse.

00:00:12.217 --> 00:00:15.757
One touch... and the light burst forth.

00:00:15.837 --> 00:00:21.639
The lesson became an adventure, and the screen an enchanted island.

00:00:21.719 --> 00:00:25.711
A glowing river, and a secret waiting.

00:00:25.791 --> 00:00:31.141
A drop of water given with a kind heart... opens the doors to treasure.

00:00:31.221 --> 00:00:38.381
Biology is a living forest, physics a glowing universe, and math a world to discover.

00:00:38.461 --> 00:00:42.453
And with the right answer... the hero wins.

00:00:42.533 --> 00:00:47.883
Then he returns... thirsty for knowledge, not running from it.

00:00:47.963 --> 00:00:53.765
PlayVerse: learn, play, compete — on every platform.

00:00:53.845 --> 00:00:59.647
And through the PlayVerse app, you enter worlds without limits.

00:00:59.727 --> 00:01:03.720
A gateway to every passion and every kind of knowledge.

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:07.792
One touch... and curiosity catches fire.

00:01:07.872 --> 00:01:14.127
Literature is told like a story, and science dances in your hands.

00:01:14.207 --> 00:01:18.651
From your seat... straight into the heart of the adventure.

00:01:18.731 --> 00:01:23.629
You learn together, no matter how far apart you are.

00:01:23.709 --> 00:01:27.701
And every correct answer... is a new victory.

00:01:27.781 --> 00:01:33.131
PlayVerse: your world to learn, play and compete.

00:01:33.211 --> 00:01:35.846
The exam is hard.

00:01:35.926 --> 00:01:41.275
With us... you are not just a student, you are a warrior.

00:01:41.355 --> 00:01:44.443
The exam is not hard.

00:01:44.523 --> 00:01:49.420
This is no barrier to my will!
